high_descs: get the soap bar from the cabinet below the sink
take the soap bar to the sink
put the soap in the sink, fill the sink with water, then drain and remove
take the soap bar over to the tub basin
drop the soap bar in the tub
anns.task_desc: get the soap form the cabinet, rinse it in the sink then put it in the tub

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the sink on the left.
Open the cabinet on the left below the sink and take out the bar of soap, then close the cabinet.
Walk over to the sink on the right.
Put the bar of soap in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn to the left and walk to the bath tub.
Put the bar of soap in the bath tub basin, to the right of the purple cloth on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned bar of soap in a bath tub.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the left sink.
Take the soap from in the left cabinet under the left sink.
Bring the soap to the right sink on the right.
Wet the soap in the sink with water.
Bring the soap to the tub on the left.
Put the soap in the tub in between the rags.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap in the tub.
